DT Dobie Kenya put together a grand gala dinner to mark the launch of the new Mercedes E-Class four door luxury saloon.The launch was held at the Arboretum Gardens, Nairobi on Thursday evening with a spectacular pyrotechnic display.The latest E-Class is the fifth generation of one of the most successful executive cars.Among those in attendance included former PS Dorothy Angote, Easy Coach MD Azym Dossa, Alibhai Shariff and Sons CEO Rafiq Shariff and East African Safari Classic director Raju Kishinani.